cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.IR 

The paper focuses on automated visual recognition for dogs, specifically face recognition. This falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) as it involves machine learning algorithms. The paper also compares different methods and solutions, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper discusses the use of datasets and image retrieval, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR).
